{"tid":2170950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：食衞局局長陳肇始同一友人加工人行宜家違反限聚令","createTime":"2020-08-23T15:14:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T03:39:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":664,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb226818f5acbbcaa9e2f0a9d2d6c78ca618e02","tid":2170950,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"今日下晝4點幾讀者Ken就影到佢現身銅鑼灣鬧市IKEA，一時睇花，一時同朋友談笑風生，身邊仲有一位工人姐姐幫手拎戰利品，惹來「3人行」疑雲。<br />\n<br />\n食衞局回覆我哋話，局長今日外出只有一位同行人士，所以冇違反限聚令。睇返599G章《規例》，同住家人一齊出街或者坐私家車係可以獲得豁免嘅，未知陳局長今日係咪淨係同好姊妹行街，唔識嗰位工人姐姐，同佢冇抱有共同目的得到豁免喇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200823/Z2CM6DXABNFIVMKB4PC3MBQXXA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200823%2FZ2CM6DXABNFIVMKB4PC3MBQXXA%2F&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=701d42d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200823%2FZ2CM6DXABNFIVMKB4PC3MBQXXA%2F&h=a91a397f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200823/Z2CM6DXABNFIVMKB4PC3MBQXXA/</a>"},{"pid":"af0beff3855608676ba7926c09077acce3b55fdf","tid":2170950,"uid":87780,"like":223,"dislike":1,"score":222,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T15:19:22.000Z","msg":"一個推車 一個拎貨 一個望地下<br />\n咪冇共同目的<br />\n冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71a3f0b6938d05d89bdb4c7e787f5ed338da971","tid":2170950,"uid":134683,"like":7,"dislike":104,"score":-97,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"冇片證實佢哋3個係識既、一齊行緊同有交流過<br />\n就咁得張硬照砌佢唔死架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e825197ed2fb8abe7ca014dc915a87aad4731ee7","tid":2170950,"uid":166729,"like":139,"dislike":1,"score":138,"quote":{"pid":"d71a3f0b6938d05d89bdb4c7e787f5ed338da971","tid":2170950,"uid":134683,"like":7,"dislike":104,"score":-97,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"冇片證實佢哋3個係識既、一齊行緊同有交流過<br />\n就咁得張硬照砌佢唔死架喎<img